quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  6,45,"Motero maziko a anthu ochimwa adaonongedwa. Ndipo kutamandidwa konse kukhale kwa Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengezedwa zonse"
  6,46,"Nena: “Tandiuzani! Ngati Mulungu akadakulandani kumva kwanu, kuona kwanu ndi kutseka mitima yanu, kodi pali mulungu wina, woonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni, amene angakubwezereni zimenezi?” Taonani mmene tifotokozera chivumbulutso chathu ndi mmene iwo sakhulupilira"
  6,47,"Nena: “Ndiuzeni, ngati chilango cha Mulungu chitadza mwadzidzidzi kapena moonekera, kodi ndani angaonongeke kupatula anthu ochita zoipa?”"
  6,48,"Ndipo Ife sititumiza Aneneri koma kuti azikawauza anthu nkhani yabwino ndi kuwachenjeza. Motero aliyense amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino, iye sadzakhala ndi nkhawa kapena kudandaula"
  6,49,"Koma iwo amene akana chivumbulutso chathu, chilango chidzawapeza chifukwa cha kusakhulupilira kwawo"
  6,50,"Nena: “Ine sindili kukuuzani kuti ndili ndi chuma cha Mulungu kapena kuti ndimadziwa zinthu zobisika kapena kuti ine ndine mngelo. Ine sinditsatira china chilichonse kupatula zokhazo zimene zavumbulutsidwa kwa ine.” Nena: “Kodi munthu wakhungu ndi munthu openya angafanane? Kodi inu simungaganize?”"
  6,51,"Ndipo achenjeze iwo amene amaopa kuti adzasonkhanitsidwa kupita kwa Ambuye wawo, amene alibe wowasamalira kapena mkhalapakati woonjezera pa Mulungu, kuti akhoza kumalewa zoipa"
  6,52,Ndipo usawathamangitse iwo amene amapembedza Ambuye wawo m’mawa ndi madzulo pofuna chisangalalo chake. Iwe siudzaimbidwa mlandu pa zochita zawo ndipo nawonso sadzaimbidwa mlandu pa zochita zako ndipo ngati iwe uwathamangitsa udzakhala mugulu la anthu opanda chilungamo